Integration with Existing OSINT Workflows

```python
# Bridge between OSINT tools and AI monitoring
class OSINTAIBridge:
    def __init__(self):
        self.osint_tools = OSINTToolkit()
        self.ai_monitors = AIONMonitoringSuite()
    
    def correlate_patterns(self, osint_signals, ai_behavior):
        """
        Correlate intelligence community patterns with AI behavior
        """
        correlations = find_cross_domain_patterns(
            domain_a=osint_signals,
            domain_b=ai_behavior,
            similarity_metric="jaccard_with_temporal_weighting"
        )
        
        return self.generate_early_warnings(correlations)
```

